OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC chairman denies        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Farranging loan for Johnson 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC chairman Richard Sharp has denied  
OL,6, that he helped arrange a loan for Boris
OL,7, Johnson when he was prime minister.    
OL,9,FMr Sharp was questioned by MPs over his
OL,10,Frole in loan talks involving Mr        
OL,11,FJohnson, which came before the then-PM 
OL,12,Fnominated him to chair the BBC board.  
OL,14,FThe government has previously said Mr  
OL,15,FSharp was appointed on merit.          
OL,17,FMr Sharp told the House of Commons     
OL,18,FDigital, Culture, Media and Sport      
OL,19,Fcommittee on Tuesday he had not given  
OL,20,FMr Johnson financial advice.           
